Revision history for Perl extension Daemond::Lite.

0.17  02.10.2013
    - Child pipes buffer cleanup fix.

0.16  15.05.2013
	- Changed proc prefix to '*'. **cking linux

0.14  22.03.13
	- Add pipe-monitoring between parent and child
	- Keep vtalarm only if no EV or AE

0.13  14.03.2013
	- Add processing of recursive include config of yaml

0.12  13.02.2013
	- Added child slot info
	- Remove duplication&keep of stdout

0.11  12.02.2013
	- Fixed syslog die on unicode

0.10  07.02.2013
	- Added identification string to proc

0.09  30.01.2013
	- Fixed default getopt
	- Method option() for extracting user values from config/getopt
	- Fix config/pid param from getopt to be relative to cwd, not binary

0.08  12.12.2012
	- Rewrite getopt.
	- Temporary disable incomplete Log::Any support
	- Fix usage() in Cli
	- Lock object keys

0.01  30.11.2012
	- Initial version, derived from Daemond

